{"tid":445723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［木馬入城］支付寶殺入街市 冀年底前用戶倍增","createTime":"2017-10-23T15:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T10:29:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"f37c23506da047b3e3d6c4073f03489cc232f854","tid":445723,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"支付寶香港跟街市營運商合作，讓商販接受支付寶付款，支付寶香港表示，希望年底前用戶數量倍增。<br />\n<br />\n去街市買餸除可用現金或八達通付款外，現在有另一個選擇，去到檔攤以手機程式掃一掃二維碼便大功告成。<br />\n<br />\n有商販表示，現時平均每日有五至六筆交易透過支付寶香港進行。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶香港跟經營街市的香港街市集團推出支付服務，首個試驗地點在秀茂坪寶達邨，初期暫免交易手續費，未來兩、三個月將陸續在另外11個街市推行。<br />\n<br />\n除街市外，支付寶香港亦希望拓展其他中小商戶市場。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶港澳台區總經理李詠詩表示，現時支付寶香港有數十萬用戶，未來會繼續加強支付寶功能，期望年底前用戶數目可以倍增。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/finance/player?newsId=240530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D240530&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6d5e973d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D240530&h=25af7c7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/finance/player?newsId=240530</a>"},{"pid":"5f6db58a3b48148c8f5bb0cf8da7135fee972850","tid":445723,"uid":3117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"都on9 街市買野俾散銀/百達通快過你支那寶10倍"},{"pid":"5ad1a4a57056db6c87f5dd6be71673b20e5950ba","tid":445723,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"500蚊唱錢撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4229e3997a7d6e71aa52d6cddcc6ea1997fbc6d4","tid":445723,"uid":2054,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"一早話撚左<br />\n近年不斷洗腦話香港落後<br />\n就係要係香港推支那寶"},{"pid":"55ed25f6151b8558a67edcb7692ba4b12d84e92e","tid":445723,"uid":3117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"網民